author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session and interview of Atmosphere featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Seismic Waves
00:02:46 Interview Pt 1
00:10:36 Perfect
00:14:17 Interview Pt. 2
00:22:24 Happymess

Musicians
Sean Daley (Slug) — vocals
Anthony Davis (Ant) — DJ
Plain Ole Bill — DJ

Credits
Host -- Andrea Swensson
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
